      <heading>Short Title</heading>
      <text><code-cite path="attachments|law" doc="Kiowa Tribe Res. No. KL-CY-2024-013">This enactment</code-cite> shall be known as the "1<sup>st</sup> Amendment of the Kiowa Tribe Sponsorship Act".</text>
